   POLL (Kansas City, Mo.) _ A new poll shows Jim Talent of St.
Louis with a slight lead in the race for Missouri governor. State
Treasurer Bob Holden leads only in the KC area. By Kit Wagar. Story
will move in the ``p'' category.
</P>
