Sunday. There are many other subplots: Greene vs. KC's Tim Harden
in the men's 100 preliminaries, Marion Jones vs. Inger Miller in
the women's 100, and local prep star Muna Lee attempting to qualify
for a berth in Sydney. By Mike DeArmond. Story will move in the
