has the future of yet another anonymous individual on his hands. A
deacon at Berea Baptist Mission in Johannesburg, Kayamba deals with
the living, kicking proof of the South African AIDS crisis:
HIV-positive infants, abandoned at his church's ``door of
hope.''....By Alex Duval Smith, The Independent &QL;
