<P>
   &UR; PATTY _ OR PATSY _ HEARST? &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; PATTY-HEARST-INDEPENDENT &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ When Patty Hearst made her stunning transformation
from society heiress to urban terrorist in the mid-1970s, she
described her family as ``capitalist pigs'' and urged them to
redistribute their ill-gotten millions to the poor. Now, a society
heiress once again, she is embracing her family with open arms _
just as her guerilla past is rushing to catch up with her....By
Andrew Gumbel, The Independent &QL;
</P>
