<P>
   FILM-REVIEW-XMEN (Undated) _ ``X-Men'' is a dead-serious,
dead-smart twist on the Marvel comics series. While X-Men fanatics
may pick nits over backstory revisionism and cropped
characterizations, this smooth, dark and consistently entertaining
``X-Men'' stays as true to the spirit of its source material as any
