<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-14 12:01 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1897 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r f BC-CAREER-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      07-14 0684
