   REUNITE _ DOTHAN, Ala. - During WWII, three American soldiers
found a baby alone in a house in Germany and returned him too his
mother. Fifty-five years and many letters later, the three will be
reunited with the 'baby' in Dothan Ala. (Manuel, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). WITH PHOTOS.
