<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-14 13:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1964 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k BC-MORSE-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      07-14 0517
