<P>
   THOUGHT GIVEN TO ELECTION BY REGISTERED VOTERS
</P>
<P>
   ................................1992......1996......2000
</P>
<P>
   Quite a lot...................63..........55..........46
</P>
<P>
   Some/little/none..........46..........45..........54
</P>
