<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    VOTERS SHOWING RECORD LEVEL OF APATHY
 &HT;    460&AMP;add. With VOTERS-DATA Moving in (w) Washington and (p)
politics categories.
 &HT;    By CHARLES W. HOLMES
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Voters are more disengaged in the presidential race
