<TEXT>
<P>
   The Fort Worth Star-Telegram plans to move the following stories
for clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of
Saturday, July 15, and thereafter. If you have any questions,
please call Lou Hudson or Carmelita Bevill on the Star-Telegram's
