<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-VOTERS-0715-1stLD-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    VOTERS SHOWING RECORD LEVEL OF APATHY
 &HT;    EDS: Resending to fix transmission garble
 &HT;    460&AMP;add.
 &HT;    With VOTERS-DATA Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics
categories.
