<HEADLINE>
PHOTO:
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the New York Times News Service Macintosh graphics
scheduled for Saturday, 07/15/2000. They are available to all NYT
graphic clients via satellite on Associated Press GraphicsNet, and
will be posted on PressLink, Newscom and the Wieck PhotoDatabase web
sites. For retransmission of graphics from the AP, call the AP
Service Desk at 212-621-7983.
</P>
<P>
   Non-subscribers may make individual graphics purchases or get
additional information by calling the NYT Photo/Graphics desk at
(212) 556-4204 or (888) 603-1036 between noon and 10 p.m. EDT.
</P>
<P>
   GENERAL
</P>
<P>
   TURKEY_Locator map -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- (BC-TURKEY-HEAT-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Locator map
