<P>
   RUSSIA-PUTIN _ NIZNY TAGILL, Russia _ Attempting to spit shine
the image of its beleagured military, Russia this week launched its
largest arms bazaar, while rows about the future of the armed
forces boiled over into the public arena. Both President Putin and
top generals spoke out on controversial proposals to restructure
the military that could change the nuclear balance of power with
the United States add resuscitate the country's military industrial
complex. (Coker, Cox News Service)
