u w BC-MIDEAST-SUMMIT-0715-C     07-14 0868
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MIDEAST-SUMMIT-0715-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SABBATH BRINGS WELCOME BREAK AT SUMMIT AS TENSION GROWS
 &HT;    With MIDEAST-JERUSALEM-0715
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
 &HT;    By BOB DEANS 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
